		      (SERPENT SCALES SNAKE-SCALES-PSEUDO)>)>

<ROUTINE SNAKE-EYE-PSEUDO ()
	 <REDIRECT ,PSEUDO-OBJECT ,EYES>>

<ROUTINE SNAKE-SCALES-PSEUDO ()
	 <COND (<OR <VERB? EXAMINE>
		    <HOSTILE-VERB?>>
